import {
  Container,Row,Col//,UncontrolledDropdown,DropdownItem,DropdownMenu,DropdownToggle
} from 'reactstrap';

const Layout = () => {
    return (
        <Container>
          <Row>
            <Col>.col</Col>
          </Row>
          <Row>
            <Col>.col</Col>
            <Col>.col</Col>
            <Col>.col</Col>
            <Col>.col</Col>
          </Row>
          <Row>
            <Col xs="3">.col-3</Col>
            <Col xs="auto">.col-auto - variable width content</Col>
            <Col xs="3">.col-3</Col>
          </Row>
          <Row>
            <Col xs="6">.col-6</Col>
            <Col xs="6">.col-6</Col>
          </Row>
          <Row>
            <Col xs="6" sm="4">.col-6 .col-sm-4</Col>
            <Col xs="6" sm="4">.col-6 .col-sm-4</Col>
            <Col sm="4">.col-sm-4</Col>
          </Row>
          <Row>
            <Col sm={{ size: 6, order: 2, offset: 1 }}>.col-sm-6 .col-sm-order-2 .col-sm-offset-2</Col>
          </Row>
          <Row>
            <Col sm="12" md={{ size: 8, offset: 2 }}>.col-sm-12 .col-md-6 .col-md-offset-3</Col>
          </Row>
          <Row>
            <Col sm={{ size: 'auto', offset: 1 }}>.col-sm .col-sm-offset-1</Col>
            <Col sm={{ size: 'auto', offset: 1 }}>.col-sm .col-sm-offset-1</Col>
          </Row>
        </Container>
      );
};
  
export default Layout;
